Implementation plan

### Big picture

**Short answer**: Start by making the thermodynamic setup configurable in code (instead of hard‑coded in `dna_nn_tm`), then validate/replicate the Allawi 1997 Tm behavior, then expose those configuration knobs (profiles + experimental arguments) to the Python API and CLI. Many of your TODOs are essentially different layers on top of “make thermodynamic parameters configurable”.

